  <scopecontent id="aspace_eb04987e7e60b603ba3084d5f93af0a9">
    <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
<p>The collection consists mainly of research files collected by Miriam Frank and Desma Holcomb for their book, <emph render="italic">Pride at Work</emph>. Also included are the organizational files, petition files, LGLN Newsletter, DC 37 Committee, and the Lesbian and Gay Teachers Association newsletter.</p>  </scopecontent>
